---
/**
 * Author bio box for blog posts.
 * Creates internal link to /about/ and contextual links to social/books.
 */
---

<div class="mt-10 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 items-start">
  <div class="flex-shrink-0">
    <a href="/about/" class="block">
      <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold">
        LB
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="flex-1">
    <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">
      <a href="/about/" class="hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors">Luca Berton</a>
    </h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">
      AI & Cloud Advisor with 18+ years experience. Author of 
      <a href="/books/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">8 technical books</a>, 
      creator of <a href="https://www.ansiblepilot.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Ansible Pilot</a>,
      and instructor at <a href="https://www.copypastelearn.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">CopyPasteLearn Academy</a>.
      Speaker at KubeCon EU &amp; Red Hat Summit 2026.
    </p>
    <div class="flex gap-3 mt-3">
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lucaberton/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-700 transition text-sm font-medium">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/lucaberton.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-500 transition text-sm font-medium">Bluesky</a>
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@BertonLuca" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-red-600 transition text-sm font-medium">YouTube</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline text-sm font-medium">Contact →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
